  "title": "Management Trainee",
  "description": "<p>Location Downtown Core, Central Region Job Type Full Time Timing 5 Day Week</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Maintain store presentation standards consistently to create an inviting environment for customers</li><li>Keep the boutique/store clean and orderly throughout operating hours to ensure a safe and pleasant space</li><li>Replenish all stock items promptly to avoid shortages and support smooth store operations</li><li>Prepare beverages and ingredients precisely according to Jian Cha’s company recipes and quality standards</li><li>Ensure safety and cleanliness during drink preparation to prevent contamination or foreign substances</li><li>Operate the cashier station to assist customers who need help beyond self-ordering kiosks and report daily sales accurately to supervisors</li><li>Participate actively in training programs and skill development activities to improve job performance</li><li>Monitor and follow company policies and systems to support organizational expectations and compliance</li><li>Open and close the store effectively as scheduled to ensure readiness for business hours</li><li>Maintain regular attendance and demonstrate full-time commitment as essential job functions</li><li>Minimize store stock losses by delivering excellent customer service and maintaining an organized store environment</li><li>Support and enhance seamless customer service by providing REAL service to customers and collaborating effectively with co-workers</li></ul>",
